library(tidyverse)
library(janitor)
details = read_rds('../data/clean_data/details_clean.rds')
fatalities = read_rds('../data/clean_data/fatalities_clean.rds')
severe_details <- details %>%
  select(-c(episode_id, wfo, source, region_fips, end_dt, region_fips, cz_type, cz_fips, cz_name, cz_timezone, injuries_direct, injuries_indirect, deaths_direct, deaths_indirect, flood_cause, category, tor_f_scale, tor_length, tor_width, tor_other_wfo, tor_other_cz_state, tor_other_cz_fips, tor_other_cz_name, begin_azimuth, end_azimuth)) %>%
  arrange(
    desc(damage_total)
  ) %>%
  slice_head(n = 20)

severe_details %>%
  mutate(event_type = fct_reorder(event_type, damage_total)) %>%
  ggplot(mapping = aes(x = log(damage_total), y = event_type)) + 
  geom_col() + 
  labs(x = "total damage($)event type", y = "event type", title = "total damage per event type")

combined_data <- severe_details %>%
  full_join(fatalities, by = "event_id")
combined_data %>%
  group_by(event_type) %>%
  mutate(no_fatalities = n()) %>%
  ggplot(mapping = aes(x = (no_fatalities), y = log(damage_total), color = event_type, fill = event_type)) +
  geom_col() + 
  labs(
    x = "Number of fatalities",
    y = "Total Damage ($) put log thing"
  )

severe_details %>%
  mutate(
    year = year(as.Date(begin_dt))
  ) %>%
  filter(
    year >2000
  ) %>%
  group_by(year) %>%
  mutate(yearly_damage = sum(damage_total)) %>%
  ggplot(mapping = aes(x = year, y = log(yearly_damage), color = factor(event_type))) +
  geom_point(size = 1) +
  facet_wrap(~event_type, scales = "free") + 
  labs(
    x = "year", y = "total damage ($)")
